    THE PROGRAM

    PART

    1

    Program Onboarding (Week 1-2)

    Get introduced to the Program and its key partners and learn about the network you can leverage throughout the program.

    PART

    2

    Mentorship & Product Building (Week 3-8)

    Learn how to build and expand your product in the crypto space, with weekly check-ins and live lectures with subject matter experts.

    PART

    3

    Execution & GTM Prep (Week 9-11)

    The program's initial eight weeks build knowledge, network, and ideas. The final weeks focus on market entry: strategy, execution, fundraising, and investor pitch.

    PART

    4

    Investor & VC Virtual demo day (Week 12)

    The Investor & VC Virtual Demo Day where you present your product to Polkadot’s leading VCs, angels & experts.

    STRATEGIC PARTNERS

    To play, press and hold the enter key. To stop, release the enter key.

    We are looking for innovative teams developing the next generation of DeFi applications and infrastructure. Our focus is on projects that can leverage the unique capabilities of Polkadot Hub, especially in the following areas:

    • Money Markets: Builders looking to innovate on features that enhance protocol safety, capital efficiency, and value accrual mechanisms.

    • DEXs (Decentralized Exchanges): AMMs or CLOBs that integrate Polkadot Hubs optimizations to improve LP efficiency, mitigate MEV leakage, and enhance the trader's user experience (UX).

    • Perpetuals: Low-latency, capital-efficient perpetuals with integrated yield vaults for automated strategy execution.

    • Yield Protocols: Automated or AI-driven yield strategies and yield trading solutions.

    • Chain Abstraction & Onboarding: Tools that simplify the user experience, such as fiat gateways and social logins.

    • Interoperability Protocols: Solutions for cross-chain liquidity, including bridge aggregators and intent networks.

    • RWA (Real-World Asset) Protocols: Platforms for the tokenization and management of traditional financial assets.

    Teams accepted into the program receive comprehensive, hands-on support across all stages of development and growth. Key benefits include:

    • Funding: Strategic and retroactive grants, seed funding, and fee rebates.

    • Liquidity Support: Dedicated DOT liquidity incentives and guaranteed TVL at launch for selected projects.

    • GTM Advisory: Support with go-to-market initiatives, tokenomics, token listings, growth, and scaling.

    • Marketing: Promotion through Polkadot's official channels, social media strategy advisory, and exposure at conference booths.

    • Hiring: Talent matchmaking and recruiter stipends for critical hires.

    • Audits: Subsidized code audits and security reviews to ensure protocol safety.

    • Technical Mentorship: Direct access to Polkadot core developers and the opportunity to influence the protocol roadmap.

    Any team building a DeFi product that plans to launch on Polkadot Hub.

    We welcome both early-stage ideas and established protocols exploring Polkadot Hub.

    Funding tiers vary, including retroactive and milestone-based grants.

    Yes! Were especially excited to support teams from Ethereum and beyond.
